quran[44]{c,v,t}:
  37,139,"Pellet, Yuunusa kadi, ko jeyanoo…óo e Nulaa…ìe …ìen"
  37,140,Janto nde o dogirnoo ka laana hebbinaaka
  37,141,"o urbinii, o jeyaa e foolaa…ìe …ìen"
  37,142,"Linngii ngii mo…ói mo, ko o felnii…óo"
  37,143,Si wanaano tawde himo jeyanoo e subbunhinotoo…ìe …ìen
  37,144,"o √±ii…ìayno e reedu maggii, haa √±alnde …ìe immintinoytee"
  37,145,"Men werlii mo ka ladde, ko o nawnu…óo"
  37,146,"Men fu…óini e mayre, leggal buudi"
  37,147,"Men nuli mo e ujune teemeder yim…ìe, maa ko …ìuri"
  37,148,"∆Åe gom…óini, Men dakmiti …ìe haa e dumunna"
  37,149,"Lamndii …ìe:\" E ko Joomi maa woodanta …ìi…ó…ìe rew…ìe, kam…ìe kan wor…ìe"
  37,150,"Kaa Men tagir Malaa'ika'en rew…óinaa…ói, hara ko …ìe seedii…ìe"
  37,151,"Faamee, kam…ìe e pepindaale ma…ì…ìe …óen, hi…ìe wi'a"
  37,152,"Allah jibinii\"; pellet, …ìe fanay"
  37,153,Hara O su…ìay …ìi…ó…ìe rew…ìe …ìen e dow wor…ìe …ìen
  37,154,"Ko he…ìi on, si …óon √±aawira non"
  37,155,E on miijitottaako
  37,156,Kaa hi…óon jogii hujja …ìanngu…óo
  37,157,"Haray addee deftere mon nden, si wonii ko on goongu…ìe"
  37,158,"∆Åe wa…ói hakkunde Makko e Malaa'ika'en, asko; hara non, Malaa'ka'en no anndi, …ìen ko tawnoytee…ìe (ka lepte)"
  37,159,"Senayee woodani Allah, e kon ko …ìe sifotoo"
  37,160,Si wanaa jeyaa…ìe Allah la…ì…ìinaa…ìe …ìen
  37,161,Anndon onon e ko rewoton kon
  37,162,"on wonaali majjinoo…ìe …óum [go…ó…óo goo]"
  37,163,si wanaa taw…óo on ko naatoowo ka Dul…ìaynge
  37,164,"[Malaa'ika'en wi'i]: \"Alaa e amen, mo alanaa …óum, darorde anndaande"
  37,165,Ko menen woni saffinaa…ìe …ìen
  37,166,Ko menen kadi woni subbunhinotoo…ìe …ìen
  37,167,∆Åe woniino e wi'ugol
  37,168,"Hara Deftere iwnde e adinoo…ìe …ìen, no woodannoo men"
  37,169,men wonayno jeyaa…ìe Allah la…ì…ìinaa…ìe
  37,170,"∆Åe yeddi nde, kono aray …ìe anndoya"
  37,171,"Gom…óii Konngol Amen ardinoke, fii jeyaa…ìe Amen, Nulaa…ìe …ìen"
  37,172,"wonnde pellet, ko kam…ìe woni walletee…ìe …ìen"
  37,173,"e wonnde ko konu Amen ngun, woni fooloo…ìe …ìen"
  37,174,"∆äuurno …ìee, haa e saanga"
  37,175,"ndaaraa …ìe, …ìe aray yi'ude"
  37,176,E hara ko lepte Amen …óen …ìe he√±orta
  37,177,"Si …óe jippike ka tannde (dingiral)ma…ì…ìe, haray bimmbi waajonoo…ìe …ìen bonii"
  37,178,"∆äuurno …ìee, haa e saanga"
  37,179,"ndaaraa, …ìe aray yi'ude"
  37,180,"Senayee woodanii Joomi maa, Jey…óo teddungal, e kon ko …ìe sifotoo"
  37,181,Kisyee wonii e Nulaa…ìe …ìen
  37,182,"Yettoore woodani Allah, Jey…óo winndere nden"